{"tid":1666984,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣可以開心啲？","createTime":"2019-10-21T08:15:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T16:32:10.000Z","uid":105055,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"4052e430f2b4567bffd47658de0b8c2c3e9c41e4","tid":1666984,"uid":105055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:15:31.000Z","msg":"依幾個月拍拖拍得好辛苦<br />\n拍得好唔開心 仲要成日睇對方面色<br />\n我覺得佢冇咁著緊我 冇以前咁想令我開心<br />\n依加一齊反而我覺得有種無形嘅壓力<br />\n明明之前唔係咁<br />\n以前真係好開心...<br />\n<br />\n每一次我講出嚟 佢都會晦氣講對唔住 但從來冇解決過個問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多次問自己 點解仲要一齊<br />\n明明大家咁唔開心 <br />\n我成日都自己屈住屈住好辛苦 成個人好抑鬱<br />\n所以成日都好想試下做啲瘋狂嘅事<br />\n但我真係唔想離開佢 <br />\n我好愛佢 我真係當佢係一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日都諗我地幾時可以結婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我真係唔知要點 <br />\n我唔知我忍到邊個位會想放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似睇唔到將來<br />\n我只係想拍拖可以好開心好sweet咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇人可以教我點可以開心啲"},{"pid":"fccf9439c6a970c3dd6585cdfa2ed1bb5bde013a","tid":1666984,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:15:41.000Z","msg":"[突發]今晚18區都有野搞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1666302\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1666302</a>"},{"pid":"b05be5035e53e039732fc555a6ec01262df155da","tid":1666984,"uid":217542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:18:17.000Z","msg":"[突發] 北角好似有手足出事<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1665948\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1665948</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n幫手推 冇媒體報導 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"855437871e1e75abad10644df557f0d80fb9820e","tid":1666984,"uid":151451,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:28:43.000Z","msg":"兩個人拍拖一定會有拗撬啦<br />\n唔好咁易放棄住 認真同佢講吓個問題 睇吓佢肯唔肯徹底改過？<br />\n唔好咁易放棄啦 <br />\n雨過就會天晴㗎喇<br />\n<br />\n唔想呢個世界上再有人分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93517aa0e1cbb9b788be173c4c278f737850ad55","tid":1666984,"uid":228894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:30:54.000Z","msg":"跟騫妹學跳開心舞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfbdac830b4b6cb62196fc00649d438ae75b89b9","tid":1666984,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T08:43:17.000Z","msg":"[實用]    香城online防具升級詳細篇<br />\n<br />\n近呢一個月，我見到多左好多新入香城online嘅玩家，勇武/和理非都有好多工作做，鑑於有好多人唔知點配搭防具，眼見好多手足都只用貴價6092X，除左冇必要之外仲晒左好多錢，故此我係度再講一次點去配合適的防具。<br />\n<br />\n防毒面具：<br />\n中後/後防(物資站/噴漆師/文宣組/美化工程組/網上資訊組)<br />\n首選最合符經濟效益<br />\n包括單咀<br />\n3200/HF-52+3311K-55<br />\n一set最平100港幣有找<br />\n雙咀：<br />\n6200+6001/6003/6005(6005唔需要特登買，成本價貴)+5n11/5p71(唔建議5p71,如果要嘅不如買502再搭P100綿抵啲)+501蓋<br />\n例如：6200+6001CN+5n11+501 我見100已經有一set<br />\n而且 就算唔用5n11同501蓋 都ok 6001CN一對最平$30，我見$50通常都有<br />\n6003貴少少 $70成平價(睇你有冇運見到)<br />\n以上都可以頂到TG，但記得聞到味要即換<br />\n<br />\n想了解更多快啲入去連登睇啦😛<br />\n...<br />\n防毒面具篇完<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1666931\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1666931</a>"},{"pid":"9bf547de16f6db4def6c16dc6b3fb1017efe05ce","tid":1666984,"uid":315121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:20:06.000Z","msg":"我都一樣 就黎痴線 <br />\n我其實都有同佢溝通過 <br />\n但個問題好似都係解決唔到 <br />\n但又唔捨得分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好辛苦 屈住屈住"},{"pid":"57af67bad89eb8697866458391ab26440516a755","tid":1666984,"uid":105055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"