心 <br />\n我成日都自己屈住屈住好辛苦 成個人好抑鬱<br />\n所以成日都好想試下做啲瘋狂嘅事<br />\n但我真係唔想離開佢 <br />\n我好愛佢 我真係當佢係一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成日都諗我地幾時可以結婚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我真係唔知要點 <br />\n我唔知我忍到邊個位會想放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似睇唔到將來<br />\n我只係想拍拖可以好開心好sweet咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇人可以教我點可以開心啲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T12:00:12.000Z","msg":"你好，這是《自殺．自療．互助舍》。看來你已累積了不少負面情緒，是嗎？人就好像氣球一樣，若積存的鬱結和壓力太多，便會有爆發的一天。何不暫時停一停，<a href=\"http://到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%88%B0%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E7%9A%84%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.help4suicide.com.hk&d=IZFSAkWTwbXSesVVmoeERU9C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=e6a193e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。 那裡有一些勵志故事和有趣短片，你可以隨心看看。你也可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），讓我們的義工為你加油打氣！<br />\n <br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！"},{"pid":"08de2e3115ed53632c3e44dc37a9767b1ea29c2b","tid":1666984,"uid":179751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T12:12:17.000Z","msg":"接近完全一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a0d45ddd88de142fb761ebadb1fdbdeab54f070","tid":1666984,"uid":105055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08de2e3115ed53632c3e44dc37a9767b1ea29c2b","tid":1666984,"uid":179751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T12:12:17.000Z","msg":"接近完全一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T16:10:21.000Z","msg":"你係咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/n